# Installation Guide

## Hardware Setup
1. Download the PCB files from the `hardware/PCB` folder.
2. Send the PCB files to a manufacturer (e.g., JLCPCB).
3. Purchase components based on the provided Bill of Materials (BOM.md).
4. Assemble the hardware according to the provided diagrams.

## Software Setup
1. Clone the repository:  
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/elderly-smartphone
   cd elderly-smartphone
